1. *Prijem* je bio uspešan. (The reception was a success.)
2. Ona je za *prijem* obukla lepu haljinu. (She wore a beautiful dress for the reception.)
3. On je pre *prijema* čitao knjigu. (He read a book before the reception.)
4. *Prijam* je trajao tri sata. (The reception lasted three hours.)
5. *Prijem* je obuhvatio sve njegove prijatelje. (The reception included all his friends.)
6. Svi su bili srećni tokom *prijema*. (Everyone was happy during the reception.)